559
00:49:32,218 --> 00:49:33,058
Good morning!

560
00:49:33,138 --> 00:49:35,018
-Good morning.
-Hello.

561
00:49:35,098 --> 00:49:36,598
-Hello, sir.
-Good morning, sir.

562
00:49:37,098 --> 00:49:38,108
Good morning, sir.

563
00:49:55,458 --> 00:49:58,578
Why do you keep calling me?
