623
00:55:26,448 --> 00:55:27,788
Will you marry me?

624
00:56:03,528 --> 00:56:04,448
I love you.

625
00:56:05,578 --> 00:56:06,778
I love you too.

626
00:56:29,928 --> 00:56:30,848
Let's go.

